title: 443.26 RATES FOR RUBBISH DISPOSAL, CITIES FIRST CLASS.
text: Any city of the first class in the state of Minnesota, in addition to the powers conferred upon it by its charter or any law of this state, is hereby authorized to establish rates for the removal, collection, and disposal from public or private property of rubbish, and to collect the same in the manner set forth in sections 443.26 to 443.35.
